z-fighting.  \\n• Desks/chairs placed on the floor with generous 0.6 m lateral aisles and 1.1 m longitudinal walkways; the rear chairs remain 0.65 m clear of the south wall.  \\n• All seats face the whiteboard (+Z); the teacher chair faces students (–Z).  \\n• Ceiling lights are symmetrically distributed around the projector with 0.4 m fixtures hanging just below the 3 m wall height—no ceiling collisions.  \\n• Bookshelf depth leaves 0.15 m clearance from the west wall; waste bins and plant occupy unused corners without obstructing aisles.  \\n• Object dimensions maintain realistic human
